  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/5e25d2d8507c41466da499f6bf1f444f.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/a50383f6a2c3889c91d69f88a7475f10.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birdfull is a small relaxing idle game. Attract birds with feed, try to keep them longer, and discover all of them including the unique ones! Watch the birds, generate more eggs in real time, and customize your cozy bird space. Try spotting all the birds of the American backyard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect birds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed the birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade feed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build facilities and decorations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing sounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute birds!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/7209c3eaa32ea394755a59e087ef3ee7.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=111 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >== Special features ==</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form loving couples and get more valuable eggs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birds won't stay forever unless you keep them fed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build special facilities to keep birds longer or forever even</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your backyard and increase your chances to see rare birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock achievements to find special kinds of birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't sell birds -they are free creatures!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/a50383f6a2c3889c91d69f88a7475f10.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birdfull is a small relaxing idle game. Attract birds with feed, try to keep them longer, and discover all of them including the unique ones! Watch the birds, generate more eggs in real time, and customize your cozy bird space. Try spotting all the birds of the American backyard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect birds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed the birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade feed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build facilities and decorations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing sounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute birds!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/7209c3eaa32ea394755a59e087ef3ee7.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=111 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >== Special features ==</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form loving couples and get more valuable eggs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birds won't stay forever unless you keep them fed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build special facilities to keep birds longer or forever even</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your backyard and increase your chances to see rare birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock achievements to find special kinds of birds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't sell birds -they are free creatures!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
